import './App.css'; import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import { Link, useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import axios from "axios"; import Header from "./Components/Header"; import Footer from "./Components/Footer"; function YeniTahsilat() { const navigate = useNavigate(); const [customer, setCustomer] = useState(); const [price, setPrice] = useState(); const [currency, setCurrency] = useState(); const [date, setDate] = useState(); const [order, setOrder] = useState(); const [explain, setExplain] = useState(); const [customers, setCustomers] = useState([]); const [currencies, setCurrencies] = useState([]); const [orders, setOrders] = useState([]); const myButtonClick = async () => { let requestBody = { Müşteri: customer, Tutar: price, ParaBirimi: currency, TahsilatTarihi: date, IlgiliSiparis: order, Aciklama: explain } const response = await axios.post( 'https://private-dfab49-nursenozcan.apiary-mock.com/Tahsilat', requestBody ); let DonusDegeri = response.data.message; alert(DonusDegeri); navigate('/YeniTahsilat', { replace: true }); } useEffect(() => { const getAllCurrencies = async () => { let response = await axios.get( 'https://private-06fa8f-currency16.apiary-mock.com/currency' ); // console.log("getAllCurrencyInfo" + response.data.CurrencyList); setCurrencies(response.data.CurrencyList); } const getAllCustomers = async () => { let response = await axios.get( 'https://private-dfab49-nursenozcan.apiary-mock.com/siparisiveren' ); // console.log("getAllCustomerInfo" + response.data.OrderedList); setCustomers(response.data.OrderedList); } const getAllOrders = async () => { let response = await axios.get( 'https://private-dfab49-nursenozcan.apiary-mock.com/ilgilisiparis' ); // console.log("getAllOrder" + response.data.OrderList); setOrders(response.data.OrderList); } // call the function getAllCurrencies().catch(console.error); // call the function getAllCustomers().catch(console.error);
